# ========================================
# AMADEUS API (Required for Flights & Cars)
# ========================================
# Get FREE test credentials (5 min):
# 1. Visit: https://developers.amadeus.com/register
# 2. Create account ‚Üí Get your API Key & Secret
# 3. Use "Test" environment for free testing
#
# Example format:
# AMADEUS_API_KEY=abcd1234efgh5678ijkl9012mnop3456
# AMADEUS_API_SECRET=Xy9ZaBcDeFgHiJkL
#
